---
// Component: OurVision
// Purpose: Vision statement with trust proof and logos.
// Props: none
// JS: none

import Eyebrow from './ui/Eyebrow.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import vexor1 from '../assets/images/vexor-1.jpg';
---

<section class="bg-brand-bg-light pt-[100px] pb-[100px] sm:py-[100px] -z-[50]">
	<div class="max-w-[1700px] mx-auto px-5 md:px-10">
		<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[2fr_3fr] gap-[60px] items-center">
			<Image
				src={vexor1}
				alt="Tworzenie stron internetowych – warsztat Vexor"
				class="reveal lg:aspect-[4/5] rounded-card object-cover w-full"
				style="--stagger-i:0"
				loading="eager"
				fetchpriority="high"
				width={800}
				height={1000}
			/>
			<div class="flex flex-col gap-[18px] min-w-0">
				<div class="reveal" style="--stagger-i:0">
					<Eyebrow label="Nasza misja" />
				</div>
				<h2 class="text-h2 reveal" style="--stagger-i:1">
					Tworzymy strony internetowe, które pracują na Twój biznes
				</h2>
				<p class="text-xl text-brand-text max-w-[620px] reveal font-400" style="--stagger-i:2">
					Każda strona którą tworzymy to wynik rozmowy o Twoim biznesie, Twoich klientach i celach sprzedażowych. Projektujemy z myślą o użytkowniku i o tym jak Google ocenia strony. Dobra strona musi ładować się szybko, działać na telefonie i być widoczna w wynikach wyszukiwania. Nasi klienci dostają stronę która generuje realne zapytania.
				</p>
				<hr class="border-brand-border reveal" style="--stagger-i:3" />
				<p class="reveal" style="--stagger-i:4">
					Pracujemy na technologiach, które gwarantują szybkość, bezpieczeństwo i wysokie pozycje w Google
				</p>
				<div class="w-full min-w-0 overflow-hidden reveal" style="--stagger-i:5">
					<div class="marquee-track flex gap-8" style="width:max-content">
						<span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-[#888] font-semibold flex-shrink-0"><img src="/icons/wordpress.svg" alt="WordPress" width="18" height="18" class="opacity-70" />WordPress</span>
						<span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-[#888] font-semibold flex-shrink-0"><img src="/icons/elementor.svg" alt="Elementor" width="18" height="18" class="opacity-70" />Elementor</span>
						<span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-[#888] font-semibold flex-shrink-0"><img src="/icons/react.svg" alt="React" width="18" height="18" class="opacity-70" />React</span>
						<span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-[#888] font-semibold flex-shrink-0"><img src="/icons/nextdotjs.svg" alt="Next.js" width="18" height="18" class="opacity-70" />Next.js</span>
						<span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-[#888] font-semibold flex-shrink-0"><img src="/icons/tailwindcss.svg" alt="Tailwind CSS" width="18" height="18" class="opacity-70" />Tailwind CSS</span>
						<span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-[#888] font-semibold flex-shrink-0"><img src="/icons/astro.svg" alt="Astro" width="18" height="18" class="opacity-70" />Astro</span>
						<span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-[#888] font-semibold flex-shrink-0"><img src="/icons/html5.svg" alt="HTML5" width="18" height="18" class="opacity-70" />HTML5</span>
						<span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-[#888] font-semibold flex-shrink-0"><img src="/icons/javascript.svg" alt="JavaScript" width="18" height="18" class="opacity-70" />JavaScript</span>
						<span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-[#888] font-semibold flex-shrink-0"><img src="/icons/typescript.svg" alt="TypeScript" width="18" height="18" class="opacity-70" />TypeScript</span>
						<span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-[#888] font-semibold flex-shrink-0"><img src="/icons/bootstrap.svg" alt="Bootstrap" width="18" height="18" class="opacity-70" />Bootstrap</span>
						<span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-[#888] font-semibold flex-shrink-0"><img src="/icons/nodedotjs.svg" alt="Node.js" width="18" height="18" class="opacity-70" />Node.js</span>
						<span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-[#888] font-semibold flex-shrink-0"><img src="/icons/mongodb.svg" alt="MongoDB" width="18" height="18" class="opacity-70" />MongoDB</span>
						<span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-[#888] font-semibold flex-shrink-0"><img src="/icons/wordpress.svg" alt="WordPress" width="18" height="18" class="opacity-70" />WordPress</span>
						<span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-[#888] font-semibold flex-shrink-0"><img src="/icons/elementor.svg" alt="Elementor" width="18" height="18" class="opacity-70" />Elementor</span>
						<span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-[#888] font-semibold flex-shrink-0"><img src="/icons/react.svg" alt="React" width="18" height="18" class="opacity-70" />React</span>
						<span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-[#888] font-semibold flex-shrink-0"><img src="/icons/nextdotjs.svg" alt="Next.js" width="18" height="18" class="opacity-70" />Next.js</span>
						<span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-[#888] font-semibold flex-shrink-0"><img src="/icons/tailwindcss.svg" alt="Tailwind CSS" width="18" height="18" class="opacity-70" />Tailwind CSS</span>
						<span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-[#888] font-semibold flex-shrink-0"><img src="/icons/astro.svg" alt="Astro" width="18" height="18" class="opacity-70" />Astro</span>
						<span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-[#888] font-semibold flex-shrink-0"><img src="/icons/html5.svg" alt="HTML5" width="18" height="18" class="opacity-70" />HTML5</span>
						<span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-[#888] font-semibold flex-shrink-0"><img src="/icons/javascript.svg" alt="JavaScript" width="18" height="18" class="opacity-70" />JavaScript</span>
						<span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-[#888] font-semibold flex-shrink-0"><img src="/icons/typescript.svg" alt="TypeScript" width="18" height="18" class="opacity-70" />TypeScript</span>
						<span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-[#888] font-semibold flex-shrink-0"><img src="/icons/bootstrap.svg" alt="Bootstrap" width="18" height="18" class="opacity-70" />Bootstrap</span>
						<span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-[#888] font-semibold flex-shrink-0"><img src="/icons/nodedotjs.svg" alt="Node.js" width="18" height="18" class="opacity-70" />Node.js</span>
						<span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-[#888] font-semibold flex-shrink-0"><img src="/icons/mongodb.svg" alt="MongoDB" width="18" height="18" class="opacity-70" />MongoDB</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
